nodes.text: Dark Horse: Phase Two is an article written by Daniel Wallace that appeared in Star Wars Insider 115. The article is a continuation of Wallace's previous article, Dark Horse Rising. Phase Two discusses how Dark Horse Comics launched multiple titles during the time when the prequel movies were released. Randy Stradley from Dark Horse explained that their sales stayed at a lower level until after Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith came out, attributing it to too many Star Wars merchandise being offered, thus forcing the fans to make choices due to limited funds.
The article was republished in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2013.
